    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "### Problem\r\n\r\n`vim.snippet.jumpable()` is a strange name and overlaps with `active()`.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nchange the signature of `vim.snippet.active()` to accept an optional `filter: { jump_dir: vim.snippet.Direction }` parameter which constrains the search to \"jumpable\" active snippet in the given direction.\r\n\r\n@MariaSolOs is there any reason this would not make sense?",
    "closed_at": "2024-04-29T20:45:54Z",
